The two Predacons, two Tripredacus and two Autobots all arrive at the cannon site. Rodimus arrives last of the six.

Rodimus: Rodimus Prime TRANSFORM!

He launches into the air, changing to bot mode. The others follow.

First Rodimus messes with some controls on the incomplete cannon. A force field is erected over it soon after.

Rodimus stands in the center of the battlefield, looking around.

&quot;Speach time,&quot; he thinks.

Rodimus Prime: You all know what is at stake here. Our possibility for survival. This cannon may be our only defense against the chaos bringer, Unicron. We cannot aford to lose it. I&#39;m sure this battle will be fierce but it is also the most importent battle any of us have fought in a long time. I want you all to look around you and notice how importent this moment will be in Cybertronian history. On this ground Autobots, Maximals, Decepticons, Predacons and Tripredacus are all united for the first time in one comon effort. We do not fight to destroy each other but to insure all of our survival. Autobots, Decepticons and otherwise, these are mere terms. We are TRANSFORMERS, a warrior race!!!!!!!

Prime draws his weapons as do the others. The ultimate battle is coming. A battle of all Transformers.


